N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 17 ยง 8153.07 - Village of Hudson Falls

State Regulations
(a) John

Street. John Street between US Route 4 and Sumpter Street in the Village of

Hudson Falls. (b) Sumpter Street. Sumpter Street between Depot Street and John Street in the Village of Hudson

Falls. (d) Prescott Avenue. Prescott Avenue between Route 254 and the Consolidated Freightways terminal on

Prescott Avenue. (e) [Eff. until

Sept. 2, 1998, see also subd. (e) below.] Route 254. Route 254 between the

Warren County/Washington county line and US Route 4 in the Village of Hudson

Falls. (e) [Eff. Sept. 2, 1998, see
also subd. (e) above.] Pearl Street. Pearl Street between US Route 4 and a
point 0.5+- mile east of US Route 4. Notes
